Class Administrator

java.lang.Object
wahoot.db.models.User
wahoot.db.models.Administrator
@Entity(name="Administrator") public final class Administrator extends User
Represents an administrator in the system, extending the User class. Administrators have additional privileges. This class maps to the "Administrator" table.
